# k8s-platform is a Helm LIBRARY chart consumed (vendored as a .tgz) by the fleet and silo charts.
# Only the chart itself ships in that package: Chart.yaml, the named templates, and the values/
# + examples/ profiles. The deploy engine and its tooling live alongside the chart in-repo but must
# NOT be packaged — without this file `helm dep update`/`build` sweeps them into the .tgz, bloating
# it from ~9 files to ~47 and shipping a substrate chart that differs from the one CI validates.
*.sh
terraform/
tests/
migrations/

# VCS / editor / OS noise (helm only applies its built-in ignore list when this file is ABSENT).
.git/
.gitignore
.DS_Store
*~
*.swp
